content:
Allow public knowledge article sharing so that Einstein can access your companyâ€™s trusted knowledge content.

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Enterprise and Unlimited Editions with the Einstein for Service add-on

From Setup, enter Knowledge Settings, select Edit, then scroll down to Share Articles via URLs Settings and select Allow users to share public articles via URLs.
Under Available Sites, move sites you want to use as a knowledge base to Selected Sites. Information from these sites is used to draft emails, so ensure you can share that information with customers.
Click Save.

Give Agents Access
title: Allowing Public Article Sharing in Salesforce
